 id=&quot;4LKvq5&quot;>;ZV-E10 II 是 APS-C 无反光镜系统相机的后续产品 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/22702421/sony-alpha-zv-e10-review-vlogging-camera-test-price-specs&quot;>;2021 年的 ZV-E10&lt;/a>;，现在配备更大的电池、26 兆像素背照式传感器，并改进了 4K 视频。 8 月初推出时，机身售价为 999 美元，与索尼新款 PZ 16-50mm f/3.5-5.6 OSS II 镜头捆绑售价为 1,099 美元，与 &lt;a href=&quot; 等旗舰手机的价格相当。 https://www.theverge.com/23899983/iphone-15-pro-max-camera-apple-full-frame&quot;>;iPhone 15 Pro Max&lt;/a>;。但是，当然，即使是最好的 iPhone 相机也有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii -vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194506/sony-alpha-zve10ii-vlogging-camera-apsc-mirrorless-specs-price</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 有较小的更新和更高的价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Flip 6 智能手机的上手照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I66riB7OyE8CUtS7R-uBM9xNMu4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452748/DSCF8089.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;炎热的可折叠夏天正如火如荼地进行，你们大家。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;opCbaW&quot;>;如果您还有任何剩余的希望，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/ 3/24191966/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-spec-leak&quot;>;泄漏&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/28/24188017/ samsung-galaxy-z-flip-fold-6-leak-renders-colors-unpacked&quot;>;泄露&lt;/a>;，三星的可折叠手机今年将进行重大更新，那么我不想成为坏消息的传播者。它们更耐用一点，更轻一点，并且有一些微小的升级。即便如此，这两款机型都获得了某种程度的提升：价格上涨，Galaxy Z Fold 6 现在的起价为 1,899 美元，Z Flip 6 的起价为 1,099 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WjhfvK&quot;>;两款手机均采用专门为三星调校的 Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 芯片组，与 S24 系列一样，它们都包含七年的操作系统和安全更新支持。由于铰链设计和材料的改进，它们都更加坚固，并声称具有更好的抗跌落能力。内部柔性玻璃也更耐用，而且...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z- Fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24195165/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-flip-6-screen-battery-price</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Watch Ultra 上手体验：超级似曾相识</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Galaxy Watch Ultra 视图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lVAlvegcCx6horuGR3JrU5QVcC4=/0x0:4032x2688/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/73452769/galaxywatchultra4.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;肯定是松鼠画。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这是 Apple Watch Ultra，但适用于 Android。哦，Galaxy Watch 7 也在这里。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-功能价格&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195083/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-7-hands-on-features-price</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星新款 Galaxy Buds 在形式和功能上都是公然的 AirPod 克隆</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;三星 Galaxy Buds 3 / Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 的实际产品照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/26UyHrvmjER1lhrtKzJzqbOWzsE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452746/DSCF8067_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UZHf7M&quot;>;除了最新的折叠手机和可穿戴设备外，三星还推出了新款 Galaxy Buds 3 Pro 和 Galaxy Buds 3。 com/2024/7/5/24192554/someone-already-bought-samsungs-galaxy-buds3-pro&quot;>;和早期销售&lt;/a>;）证实，该公司已经放弃了过去几代的微妙入耳式设计茎状外观赋予它们类似 AirPods 的外观和感觉——尤其是白色。两款耳塞均采用青铜灰色饰面，与棱角分明的“刀片”设计相结合，让我想起了特斯拉的 Cyber​​truck。但不可否认的是，它与苹果广受欢迎的 AirPods 总体上有相似之处。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;D8k3an&quot;>;三星的新闻稿称，这一转变是“收集到的各种统计数据”的直接结果，这些数据表明柄形因素可产生更好的舒适度和入耳稳定性。所以，我们在这里......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24195011/samsung-galaxy-buds-3-pro-hands-on-preview-features</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Ring 可能是统治生态系统的唯一戒指</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在盒子中持有 Galaxy Ring 的人&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YcBPYKFtyCgjtA6ayg_yQa0HEwg=/0x0:8064x5376/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73452758/galaxyring5.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;售价 399.99 美元，无需订阅，从 7 月 24 日开始正式发售。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;硬件很坚固。这些想法很有趣。只要在测试中表现出色，三星就有可能获胜。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price -unpacked-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price-unpacked-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24194938/samsung-galaxy-ring-hands-on-price-unpacked-2024</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:32:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:32:17-04:00</updated><title>三星 Galaxy Unpacked：夏季产品活动的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、蓝色和水绿色背景上的三星徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/j30lXEiclgq_A3r3_h4CIMAulZo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452722/acastro_STK075_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;三星准备谈论可折叠设备和人工智能，甚至可能还有更多。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194881/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-ring-ai-z-fold-6-flip-watch-7-ultra-buds</id><author><name>宋茜</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:20:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:20:00-04:00</updated><title>智能家居如何搬家</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;起重机将大脑移出智能家居的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RpIoVtoh6HQXRpRzLi93guAMPlY=/1x0:3481x2320/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452698/247132_SMART_HOME_MOVE_JGibbs.0.jpg ” />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Jackson Gibbs for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;搬出和搬进智能家居需要非常注重细节。本指南将帮助您完成它。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24184716/moving-smart-home-tech-setup</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:00:13-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:00:13-04:00</updated><title>塑料垃圾箱：比盒子更好</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;插图：两名专业搬运工搬运装在即将散架的纸板箱中的物品。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sQMeGeuHX7pBJln9y_rWxvkvzi4=/0x1：4054x2704/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452675/247132_CARDBOARD_BOXES_JGibbs.0。 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Jackson Gibbs for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;租用垃圾箱很方便，更可持续，而且我一次也没有错过纸板箱。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes- Plastic-bins-cardboard&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes-plastic-bins-cardboard" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24176469/moving-boxes- Plastic-bins-cardboard</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-10T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-10T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 《遣散费》第二季将于 1 月开播——这是第一个预告片</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《Severance》第二季剧照。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i2Ihs_4wgOv-daht1PdGhySWVZI=/716x0:3125x1606/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73452644/SEV2_first_look_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;59SmZ0&quot;>;“音乐舞蹈体验”正在回归。 Apple 刚刚发布了万众期待的《Severance》第二季的首支预告片，并有消息称该剧要到 2025 年才会回归。第一集将在 Apple TV Plus 上开始播放1 月 17 日和最后 10 集。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;V0D2b6&quot;>;简短的预告片并没有透露太多关于新一季的内容，但据苹果公司称，“马克（亚当·斯科特）和他的朋友们了解轻视遣散费壁垒的可怕后果，让他们在悲惨的道路上走得更远。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;FsBfSn&quot;>;在预告片发布的前一天，苹果发布了一个相当神秘的预告片：&lt;/p>; >; &lt;div id=&quot;uPEUtM&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot;true&quot;align=&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;zxx&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https ://t.co/046vNV03vz&quot;>;pic.twitter.com/046vNV03vz&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;—Apple TV (@AppleTV) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/AppleTV/status/1810645085941383335 ?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;2024 年 7 月 9 日&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;LWKpsn&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22929661/severance -review-apple-tv-plus&quot;>;&lt;em>;Severance&lt;/em>; 于 2022 年在 Apple TV Plus 上首次亮相&lt;/a>;，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23268501/severance-season-2-trailer-date-apple-tv-plus&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23268501/severance-season-2-trailer-date-apple-tv-plus" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23268501/severance-season-2-trailer-date-apple-tv-plus</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry></feed>